column1: Daily Weather Observations for Murrurundi, New South Wales for March 2016
Prepared at 13:01 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW2090.201603
Most observations from Murrurundi, but some from Murrurundi Gap.
Temperature, humidity, cloud and rainfall observations are from Murrurundi Post Office {station 061051}
Wind and pressure observations are from Murrurundi Gap AWS {station 061392}
